                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18250407-86-off458 t18250407-86-cd459"></join>, a handkerchief, value 6 s., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18250407-86-victim520" type="victimName">
                        Thomas Burgh 
                        Lewis
                     <interp inst="t18250407-86-victim520" type="surname" value="Lewis"></interp>
